Right, right, right

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:39.680
This move is cool, this move is cool

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.280
Careful, careful

00:02:42.439 --> 00:02:43.159
Pick up the speed

00:02:48.439 --> 00:02:49.039
That one

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:54.520
It's good for a young man to have drive

00:02:57.319 --> 00:02:58.199
It seems this Master Ip

00:02:58.199 --> 00:02:59.080
is hard to play

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:05.120
To combine martial arts and dance

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:06.080
together

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.240
is even harder

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:13.080
Dance is about posture and rhythm

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.639
Martial arts is about power and striking

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:18.319
To merge these two things together

00:03:19.199 --> 00:03:20.680
isn't just about imitating movements

00:03:22.199 --> 00:03:23.520
We have to follow the martial arts coach first

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:24.639
and learn every move and style

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:27.400
Then slowly infuse the power into the dance

00:03:28.759 --> 00:03:29.639
But power and dance feel

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.520
are like two streams of water

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:32.919
To make them flow together

00:03:33.319 --> 00:03:35.719
you have to grind and practice repeatedly

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.360
Practiced again and again

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:40.360
still can't catch the feeling

00:03:41.520 --> 00:03:42.599
I started to panic a bit inside

00:03:44.479 --> 00:03:45.400
Even doubting

00:03:47.960 --> 00:03:48.639
if I

00:03:49.759 --> 00:03:50.919
can really do it

