Hongji

00:04:01.879 --> 00:04:03.120
Is the Ip Man training going well

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:04.400
It's okay

00:04:05.479 --> 00:04:07.879
Just can't find the character's feeling

00:04:08.319 --> 00:04:10.199
Mom believes you can definitely do it

00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:31.160
I have a dream

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:32.839
When I grow up

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:35.480
I want to go to a bigger stage

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:36.120
to dance

00:04:36.519 --> 00:04:38.279
To be the lead once

00:04:39.439 --> 00:04:40.879
Mom coming to watch me dance

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:44.120
will definitely be very happy

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:04.319
Don't cry, don't cry

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:06.439
I believe in you

00:05:06.759 --> 00:05:09.240
You will definitely dance the best in the future

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:42.360
You two rascals

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:44.560
If you don't play on the stage

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:45.920
why are you playing here

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:47.439
Are you out of your minds

00:05:47.439 --> 00:05:48.560
Let me do it. Sorry, Auntie

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:52.879
Keep practicing

00:05:53.759 --> 00:05:54.319
Okay

00:05:55.639 --> 00:05:58.759
The human mind is precarious; the mind of the Way is subtle

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:02.240
Be discriminating and unified; hold fast to the Mean

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:04.240
I wish to support and protect the people

00:06:04.439 --> 00:06:06.199
It is indeed difficult

00:06:06.439 --> 00:06:08.959
Only by overcoming difficulties can one perfect virtue

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:13.680
Dragging my tired body home every day

00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:16.199
the frustration of losing direction followed me like a shadow

00:06:16.839 --> 00:06:19.000
Just like that tango competition in my childhood

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:21.639
Mom's encouragement

00:06:21.639 --> 00:06:22.680
childhood determination

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.199
calmed me down

00:06:26.879 --> 00:06:27.759
The firmness of martial arts

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:30.560
the softness of dance

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:32.759
firmness and softness complementing each other

00:06:33.879 --> 00:06:35.120
Internal tension, external relaxation

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:36.680
Merging hardness with gentle beauty

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:38.759
Dancing out a dance language unique to China

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:16.720
At that moment, I finally understood.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.480
Dance isn't just striking a pose.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.439
And martial arts isn't just throwing punches and kicks.

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:25.360
Dance and martial arts aren't just techniques.

00:07:25.480 --> 00:07:26.240
They are a conviction.

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:29.120
The body is an extension of the heart.

00:07:34.319 --> 00:07:36.399
Mom, I think I've realized it.

00:07:37.279 --> 00:07:38.160
Every punch, every palm strike.

00:07:38.279 --> 00:07:39.319
Every step, every dance.

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:41.399
It's not simply imitating Ip Man.

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:43.560
But taking his strength as the core,

00:07:44.319 --> 00:07:46.439
and softening it into a new, modern context.

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:49.439
To truly fuse dance and martial arts

00:07:49.519 --> 00:07:51.240
together on the stage.

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:53.759
Our dance drama, "Wing Chun,"

00:07:54.519 --> 00:07:55.560
is a first.

00:07:56.519 --> 00:07:58.560
This is both a brand-new attempt

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:01.360
and a bold challenge.

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:03.120
But fusion is exactly what we want.

00:08:03.759 --> 00:08:05.360
We want breakthroughs and innovation.

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:05.879
Right?

00:08:06.279 --> 00:08:07.000
Right!

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:11.759
Mom,

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:13.759
that dream I wrote about

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:14.680
in my essays as a child...

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:16.199
Today, I've really achieved it.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.240
I want you to see for yourself

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:19.759
who I've grown up to be.

00:08:20.199 --> 00:08:22.000
To see how I stand on that stage.

