Wing Chun

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:49.559
is authentic Chinese Kung Fu.

00:08:51.679 --> 00:08:52.639
In the future, when you have the chance

00:08:52.639 --> 00:08:54.000
to stand on the world stage,

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.519
what you represent

